Package controller.hrs

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ReservationInterface
    ReservationInterface is an interface representing a generic contract for all implementing classes to expose method(s) to handle reservation logic.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CheckInCheckOutController
    CheckInCheckOutController is a controller that performs check-in check-out operations.
    CheckInPredicate
    CheckInPredicate is a predicate class that determines whether a Reservation passes or fails a check-in predicate which includes conditions such as start and end date and guest it belongs to.
    CheckOutPredicate
    CheckOutPredicate is a predicate class that determines whether a Reservation passes or fails a check-out predicate which includes conditions such as start and end date and guest it belongs to.
    ReservationController
    ReservationController is a controller that performs reservation operations.
    RoomReservationPredicate
    RoomReservationPredicate is a predicate class that determines whether a Room passes or fails a reservation predicate which includes conditions such as start and end date as well as room criteria.
